of all affected memory.

41:30.613 --> 41:32.572
Query. What have l forgotten?

41:32.781 --> 41:34.324
Can you do the same
with the Enterprise?

41:34.533 --> 41:37.160
l don't see why not, but it will have
to be a complete shutdown.

41:37.369 --> 41:39.704
We turn her off
and effect a wipe of the Yamato log

41:39.914 --> 41:42.707
